        {
          "q": "Should I stop all skincare?",
          "a": "Not necessarily, but you may need to reduce to what your skin can truly handle. Choose a gentle cleanse, fewer steps and soothing products until the barrier feels steadier."
        },
        {
          "q": "When should I see a doctor?",
          "a": "Get medical help if you have breathing trouble, swelling of the lips or face, fever, blisters, sores, a rash that spreads quickly or symptoms that do not settle. Better one extra visit than waiting too long."
        }
